re to get icons for your projects."}]}]},{"type":"step","caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Have a look "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki"},{"type":"text","text":" to discover how OUDS works."}]}],"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-6-3.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS iOS provides also a wiki attached to its GitHub repository. The wiki is a public base of knowledge with plenty of things: available API, technicala architecture, tips about processes, tests, conventions and toolings."}]}]},{"type":"step","caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To get the source code of this showcase app, go to its dedicated GitHub repository at "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios-design-system-toolbox"}]}],"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-6-4.png","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For technical reasons the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":" GitHub repository does not embed the source code of the "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"design system toolbox","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" app. In fact this app and all its snapshots for tests increases a lot the size of the repository."}]}]},{"type":"step","caption":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Do not hesitate to "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/issues"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/discussions"},{"type":"text","text":"!"}]}],"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"media":"tutorial-6-5.png","content":[{"type"